msgctxt "Talk_05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>A little while ago...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"The <2.se_co>sand seal<3.re_co> that the <4.se_co>chief<5.re_co> was\n"
"with got spooked by a monster and\n"
"ran off...\n"
"She quickly realized that it had pulled\n"
"her very close to <6.se_co>Naboris<7.re_co>...\n"
"\n"
"Anyone who approaches <8.se_co>Naboris<9.re_co> risks\n"
"being struck by lightning from that\n"
"Divine Beast.\n"
"The <10.se_co>chief<11.re_co> was lucky to get away...<12.pa> And\n"
"ever since then, Buliara has refused to\n"
"leave her side."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It's impossible to get a wink of sleep with\n"
"how noisy everyone is! All those young\n"
"ones at the canteen...\n"
"I'd like to whip their attitudes into\n"
"shape."
msgstr ""

